<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>EDU_ZONE Activation email</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">

    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #41f5ef1a;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .message-sm{
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
            padding-top: 50px;
        }
        .message-sm > h1{
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .course-info {
            margin: auto;
            padding: 20px 0px;
            width: 100%;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2), 0 6px 20px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.19);
            color: #000000;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .course-info > h4 {
            color: #0a3622;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 22px;
            font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0 !important;
            margin-top: 0 !important;
        }

        .footer{
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 100px;
            color: #0a53be;
        }

    </style>

</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-sm">
            <h1>Your ELearning order is confirmed!</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>

        <div class="course-info">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table style="border-bottom: 1px solid #0000002f;">
                <tr>
                    <td>
                        Order #: <%= order.id %>
                    </td>
                    <td>
                        Order Date:<%= order.date &>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
                <tr>
                    <td class="first-td">Item</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Qty</td>
                    <td class="first-td">Cost</td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table style="width: 90%; margin: auto; display: block">
                <tr>
                    <td class="second-td"><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td class="second-td">1</td>
                    <td class="second-td">$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #000000;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-2">Subtotal:</td>
                    <td class="col-2">$<% = order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>

            <table class="table-row" style="border-top: 1px solid #000000;">
                <tr>
                    <td class="col-2">Total:</td>
                    <td class="col-2">$<% = order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                If you have any questions, please contact our support team at
                <a href="mailto:chanuka.weerakkody123@gmail.com">chanuka.weerakkody123@gmail.com</a>
            </p>
            <p>
                <a href="#">Terms of Service</a> | <a href="#">Privacy Policy</a>
                <p>&copy; 2023 ELearning. All rights reserved</p>
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

</body>
</html>

